title: Moe, McGaffie, Kemp recall 2010 Oklahoma game
text:
Moe, McGaffie, Kemp recall 2010 Oklahoma game POSTED: 07:00 PM CDT Oct 11, 2015 UPDATED: 11:52 PM CDT Oct 11, 2015 
Almost five years have passed since Missouri's incredible homecoming victory over Oklahoma. T.J. Moe, Wes Kemp and Gahn McGaffie provide their perspective on that special day in 2010.
